               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary" (fols. 3r-34r)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fol. 3r-16v)
 I-2) ʾƎsaggǝd
                     laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... “I worship Thee ...” (fols. 16v-20r)
 I-3) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām “Miracles of Mary”: 4 miracles (fols. 20r-29v)
 I-4) Introductory
                     exhortation (fols. 29v-34r)
 II) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus”: 1
                     miracle (fols. 34v-35v)</summary>
